372
00:44:36,590 --> 00:44:37,691
Yes.

373
00:45:12,590 --> 00:45:14,800
I fought with Gyeong Mi again today.

374
00:45:15,501 --> 00:45:16,601
Gyeong Mi...

375
00:45:17,001 --> 00:45:19,941
