424
00:50:12,090 --> 00:50:15,431
By the way, why are you so interested in this Choi Sun Hui?

425
00:50:16,001 --> 00:50:18,731
She's clearly in the center of the case.

426
00:50:19,501 --> 00:50:20,771
"The case?"

427
00:50:22,570 --> 00:50:26,041
