432
00:50:35,380 --> 00:50:37,989
The house could've caught fire, and she could've run away.

433
00:50:37,990 --> 00:50:39,890
Forget it. She's moving. Follow her.

434
00:50:39,891 --> 00:50:41,460
All right. Gosh.

435
00:50:41,461 --> 00:50:44,190
