540
00:58:37,470 --> 00:58:40,840
and shook the chestnuts off to survive.

541
00:58:42,541 --> 00:58:44,070
As you know,

542
00:58:46,441 --> 00:58:48,211
I was devoted...

543
00:58:48,711 --> 00:58:50,481
to expanding...

544
00:58:50,681 --> 00:58:53,081
